## 1. Card Component Styling

### Component File
`/Users/marc/conductor/workspaces/chkit/davao/apps/docs/node_modules/@astrojs/starlight/user-components/Card.astro`

### Class Names to Target

| Element | CSS Class | Scoped Layer | Purpose |
|---------|-----------|--------------|---------|
| Card container | `.card` | `starlight.components` | Main card wrapper, uses `sl-flex` |
| Card title section | `.title` | `starlight.components` | Heading area with icon and text |
| Card icon | `.icon` | `starlight.components` | Icon styling (child of `.card .icon`) |
| Card body | `.body` | `starlight.components` | Content area |
| Card grid wrapper | `.card-grid` | `starlight.components` | Container for multiple cards |

### CSS Variables and Color Cycling

The Card component implements cycling colors based on position (every 4th card):

```css
.card {
    --sl-card-border: var(--sl-color-purple);
    --sl-card-bg: var(--sl-color-purple-low);
}

.card:nth-child(4n + 1) {
    --sl-card-border: var(--sl-color-orange);
    --sl-card-bg: var(--sl-color-orange-low);
}

.card:nth-child(4n + 3) {
    --sl-card-border: var(--sl-color-green);
    --sl-card-bg: var(--sl-color-green-low);
}

.card:nth-child(4n + 4) {
    --sl-card-border: var(--sl-color-red);
    --sl-card-bg: var(--sl-color-red-low);
}

.card:nth-child(4n + 5) {
    --sl-card-border: var(--sl-color-blue);
    --sl-card-bg: var(--sl-color-blue-low);
}
```

### Specific Selectors for Overriding

To override card colors, target:
- `.card:nth-child(4n + 1)` - Orange (1st, 5th, 9th, etc.)
- `.card:nth-child(4n + 3)` - Green (3rd, 7th, 11th, etc.)
- `.card:nth-child(4n + 4)` - Red (4th, 8th, 12th, etc.)
- `.card:nth-child(4n + 5)` - Blue (5th variant, if it cascades with +1)
- `.card` (default) - Purple

### Card Icon Styling
```css
.card .icon {
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-card-border);
    background-color: var(--sl-card-bg);
    padding: 0.2em;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
}
```

### CardGrid Styling
```css
.card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 100%;
    gap: 1rem;
}

@media (min-width: 50rem) {
    .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .stagger {
        --stagger-height: 5rem;
        padding-bottom: var(--stagger-height);
    }
    .stagger > :global(*):nth-child(2n) {
