## 6. CSS Layers and Specificity

All Starlight styles are organized in layers (for override control):

```
@layer starlight.base
@layer starlight.core
@layer starlight.components
@layer starlight.content
@layer starlight.utils
```

To override with your own styles, you should:
1. Create your styles AFTER importing Starlight
2. Target the same selectors
3. Or use `@layer overrides { }` to create a layer that comes after starlight

